cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the security and privacy concerns in deep learning, specifically focusing on adversarial attacks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses the design of adversarial attack algorithms, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
